CreateVault_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── when token zero
│  └── it should revert
└── when token not zero
   ├── when native token
   │  └── it should revert
   └── when not native token
      ├── when expiry in past
      │  └── it should revert
      ├── when expiry in present
      │  └── it should revert
      └── when expiry in future
         ├── when target price zero
         │  └── it should revert
         └── when target price not zero
            ├── when target price not exceed oracle price
            │  └── it should revert
            └── when target price exceeds oracle price
               ├── given no adapter
               │  ├── it should create the vault
               │  ├── it should deploy a share token with correct symbol
               │  ├── it should return ACTIVE status
               │  ├── it should bump the next vault ID
               │  └── it should emit a {CreateVault} event
               └── given adapter
                  ├── it should create the vault with adapter
                  ├── it should deploy a share token with correct symbol
                  ├── it should register the vault into adapter
                  ├── it should mark the vault as staked in adapter
                  ├── it should return ACTIVE status
                  ├── it should bump the next vault ID
                  └── it should emit a {CreateVault} event
